const styles = {
    button: {
        backgroundColor: '#ff007f',
        height: 60,
        flexDirection: 'row',
        borderRadius: 10,
        overflow: 'hidden',
        alignItems: 'center',
        marginTop: 8,
    },

    buttonIcon: {
        height: 60,
        width: 60,
        backgroundColor: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center'
    },

    buttonText: {
        flex: 1,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        textAlign: 'center',
        color: '#FFF',
        fontFamily: 'Roboto_500Medium',
        fontSize: 16,
    },

    container: {
        flex: 1,
        padding: 32,
        backgroundColor: '#F0F0F5'
    },

    description: {
        color: '#6C6C80',
        fontSize: 16,
        marginTop: 16,
        fontFamily: 'Roboto_400Regular',
        maxWidth: 260,
        lineHeight: 24,
        textAlign: 'center'
    },

    footer: {},

    image: {
        border: 200,
      borderColor: 'Black',
      borderRadius: 100,
      marginRight: 210,
      marginTop: -115,
      width: 110,
      height: 110
    },

    input: {
        height: 60,
        backgroundColor: '#FFF',
        borderRadius: 10,
        marginBottom: 8,
        paddingHorizontal: 24,
        fontSize: 16,
    },

    main: {
        flex: 1,
        justifyContent: 'center'
    },

    select: {},

    title: {
        color: '#322153',
        fontSize: 20,
        fontFamily: 'Ubuntu_700Bold',
        maxWidth: 260,
        marginTop: 64,
        marginLeft: 115
    },
}

export default styles;
